data.title: Jackrabbit Media
data.meta_description: Take a look at Octane Entertainment's available movies.
data.text:
POOLS

Genre: Coming-of-Age, Comedy, Drama

Stuck at summer school after flunking a year of college and suffocated by a heat wave, Kennedy (Odessa A’zion) rallies a ragtag crew for a pool hopping escape through the lavish estates of Lake Forest

SICK GIRL

Genre: Comedy

A woman’s desire for change leads to a little lie that spirals out of control, straining her friendships and dividing her community in this female-driven comedy.

BABY BLUE

Genre: Supernatural Horror, YA

A group of teens stumble across the story of a now dead serial killer and decide he’d be the perfect subject of a true crime vodcast. But when they start digging, they quickly discover that his murder spree never stopped and now they are being targeted from beyond the grave.

RIKI RHINO: THE BIRD KINGDOM

Genre: Animation

A courageous rhinoceros named Riki and his duck companion Beni embark on an exciting journey through lush jungles in search of a magical seed that can save their home from an impending tsunami.

THE ARTIFICE GIRL

Genre: Sci-Fi

When an internet vigilante develops a revolutionary new computer program to combat online predators, its rapid advancement leads to serious questions of autonomy, oppression, and what it really means to be human.

FOLLOW HER

Genre: Psychological Thriller

A struggling actress who secretly films weird encounters with strangers for fame finds herself caught up in a twisted revenge plot when she pushes the ethical boundaries of social media.

THE MENTAL STATE

Genre: Dramatic Thriller

In the heart of rural Kentucky, a high school senior and his family struggle to cope with the true identity and intentions of a dangerous town shooter.

SUMMONERS

Genre: Horror

Jessica Whitman isn’t a witch. Not anymore, at least. She left it behind when she left her hometown almost ten years ago. But when a childhood friend needs her help performing a dark spell, she’ll find herself questioning her sense of right and wrong, and grappling with her late mother’s secrets.

LA SOGA SALVATION

Genre: Action, Crime, Thriller

Years after his last hit, a skilled hitman is dragged back into his old life to take on a crew of dangerous killers, including a particularly mysterious assassin who has long waited for the chance to even the score.

SHAKY SHIVERS

Genre: Horror Comedy

Two young women find themselves at an abandoned camp in the woods with a book of magical spells surrounded by classic monsters in this comedic send up of ’80s horror films.

INFLUENCER

Genre: Thriller

While struggling on a solo backpacking trip in Thailand, social media influencer Madison meets CW, who travels with ease and shows her a more uninhibited way of living, but CW’s interest in her takes a darker turn.

ERADICATION

Genre: Horror, Thriller

When an unknown disease wipes out most of the world’s population, a man with unique blood is isolated for study. Fearing for his wife’s safety, he breaks his quarantine – into a world overrun by monstrous Infected and a shadowy agency hunting them down.

TONE DEAF

Genre: Comedy, Horror, Thriller

A woman goes to the countryside to spend a quiet weekend after losing her job and having her last complicated relationship implode. She rents a country house from an old-fashioned widower, who struggles to hide his psychopathic tendencies.

IKÉ BOYS

Genre: Action

When a magical anime transforms two Japan-obsessed teenage friends and a shy foreign exchange student into its superpowered characters, the three underdogs must discover their inner heroes in time to save the world.

GHOSTS OF THE OZARKS

Genre: Thriller/Horror

In post-Civil War Arkansas, a young doctor is mysteriously summoned to a remote town in the Ozarks only to discover that the utopian paradise is filled with secrets and surrounded by a menacing, supernatural presence.

THE TIME CAPSULE

Genre: Romance

In the near future, a politician fresh off an electoral loss escapes to his family’s summer lake house. His vacation is disrupted by the appearance of his first love, who has just returned from a 20-year space voyage and hasn’t aged a day.

ANSWER THE CALL

Genre: Comedy

Cora spends her days begrudgingly answering phones at a Prayer Call Center under the watch of well-intentioned leader Bill. When a caller shows up convinced he’s been saved by her voice, she must decide if she’s the one he thinks she is.

BEAUTIFUL DARKNESS aka LOVE IS BLIND

Genre: Action

The fantastical story of a young woman who literally cannot see her mother even though they live in

the same house, an invisible man who becomes an accidental hero, and an eccentric psychologist

grasping to make sense of it all. When you can’t trust our own eyes, sometimes, you have to believe to see.

BENEATH THE LEAVES

Genre: Thriller

A deranged kidnapper escapes prison twenty years into his sentence and none of his former victims are safe, including Detective Brian Larson. When Larson is forced off of the case he chooses to get revenge on his own. Leaving Detective Erica Shotwell no choice but to track down the convict and save her partner.

BERSERK

Genre: Thriller

Three characters make the realization that none of them have ever felt true-fear, so over the course of one night, they set out to trick each other into feeling it.

DON’T LOOK BACK

Genre: Thriller/Horror

When a young woman overcoming her traumatic past is among several witnesses who see a man fatally assaulted and don’t intervene, they find themselves targeted by someone, or something, out for revenge.

ENCOUNTER

Genre: Sci-Fi

A group of friends uncover an otherworldly object in a rural field, which they soon discover holds greater secrets than they could ever imagine.

ESCAPE FROM DEATH BLOCK 13

Genre: Action

After being framed for murder, a man agrees to become an informant during his stay at a notorious prison. Once inside, he finds that his biggest threat may not come from his fellow convicts.

HANNA’S GOLD

Genre: Family

Two sisters from Beverly Hills find themselves in the adventure of a lifetime when they’re sent to spend the summer working on a horse ranch with their estranged father. Always seeming to find trouble, they get more than they bargained for when they become involved in a heart stopping hunt for buried treasure in the mountains above the ranch.

HE’S OUT THERE

Genre: Thriller/Horror

On vacation at a remote lake house, a mother and her two young daughters must fight for survival after falling into a terrifying and bizarre nightmare conceived by a psychopath.

HOPE SPRINGS ETERNAL

Genre: Action

When 18 year old Hope Gracin’s life suddenly changes, she finds the world is unsympathetic and she must learn to live without an expiration date.

LADY-LIKE

Genre: Comedy

When a quick-witted but co-dependent college girl helps her best friend land a boyfriend, she’s left on the outside looking in and is forced to deal with the realities of adulthood for the first time.

MAYHEM

Genre: Action/Thriller

The story of a virus that infects a corporate law office on the day attorney Derek Cho (Yeun) is framed by a co-worker and wrongfully fired. Trapped in the quarantined building, our hero is forced to savagely fight tooth and nail for not only his job but his life.

MIDNIGHTERS

Genre: Thriller

Midnight, New Year’s Eve: when all the hopes of new beginnings come to life – except for Lindsey and Jeff Pittman, whose strained marriage faces the ultimate test after they cover up a terrible crime and find themselves entangled in a Hitchcockian web of deceit and madness.

MY ADVENTURES WITH SANTA

Genre: Family

Christmas in the Nolan household isn’t what it used to be. On a last minute shopping trip with Dad, the family enters an enchanted store only to discover a dazzling snow globe with magical powers.

MY SOUL TO KEEP

Genre: Action

Like many young children, Eli Braverman believes something evil lurks in his basement. One fateful night, Eli is left home alone to face his worst fear…and found out if the horror is real, or all in his mind.

OBSESSION

Genre: Thriller

Obsession is a thriller about an out-of-work mechanic named Sonny who, afte saving a wealthy man’s life, begins to fall for his wife. Soon after, a passionate affair ensues, leading to a twisted plan to take the husbands life and riches.

PAYDIRT

Genre: Action/Thriller

A parolee teams up with his old crew determined to find a buried bag of cash stolen a decade ago from a DEA bust gone bad, while being tracked by a retired Sheriff.

PUNCHING HENRY

Genre: Comedy

Hapless satirical songwriter Henry Phillips is lured to LA when a veteran TV producer decides to make a show about the life of a loser.

RAPID EYE MOVEMENT

Genre: Action/Thriller

A publicity seeking radio DJ is driven to the edge of insanity when he attempts to break the 11 day world record for staying awake-under the threat of a deranged caller who will kill him if he falls asleep.

REVENGE RIDE

Genre: Action/Thriller

When a college girl gets drugged by the local football players at her school, she joins a female motorcycle gang to take revenge on them, resulting in a bloody battle between both sides.

RUST CREEK

Genre: Thriller

After her car breaks down on a back country road, a resourceful young woman must evade and outsmart a group of local criminals in order to survive.

RYDE

Genre: Thriller/Horror

Technology brings us closer. Or perhaps it brings strangers, a little too close. But how much can you really trust someone? With a new ride share service, you never know who will be getting in a car with. Or if you’ll ever get out.

SPACEMAN

Genre: Comedy/Drama

When an outspoken major league veteran loses his job after walking off the team to protest the firing of a teammate, he spirals downward while desperately trying to catch on with another pro team, until he finds true freedom playing the game for himself.

ST. AGATHA

Genre: Action

A pregnant con woman on the run seeks refuge in a convent hidden in deafening isolation. What first starts out as the perfect place to have a child turns into a dark lair where silence is forced, ghastly secrets are masked, and every bit of will power is tested. She soon learns the sick and twisted truth of the convent and the odd people that lurk inside its halls.

TELL ME HOW I DIE

Genre: Thriller

When a group of college students take part in a clinical drug trial, an unexpected side effect of the experimental medicine gives them terrifying visions of their own deaths…which begin to come true. As they scramble to escape their fate, they discover that the killer is among them and shares their ability to see the future – only he seems to be one step ahead of their efforts to survive.

THE BLUE SKELETON

Genre: Thriller/Horror

Recovering from the trauma of being kidnapped last Halloween by the Blue Skeleton – a group who take “extreme haunt” to another level – five friends decide they must face their fears in order to move on. Heading back out on the road to visit more haunted house attractions, signs of the Blue Skeleton start appearing again and a new terror begins.

THE COTTAGE

Genre: Thriller

When Chloe (Kristen Dalton) and Michael Carpenter rent out the cottage behind their house to charming romance novelist, Robert Mars (David Arquette) their American dream soon turns into a suburban nightmare.

THE AMITYVILLE HARVEST

Genre: Thriller/Horror

A documentary crew is invited to a historic farm house in Amityville to conduct important interviews of a famed historian. One by one, they begin to break the rules of the house and witness strange and unholy events.

THE AMITYVILLE MOON

Genre: Thriller/Horror

A Detective is hired to find two runaway girls from a Boarding Home run by the Church. After finding and returning one of the girls, the Detective discovers a horrifying secret of the Home, a Werewolf killing and eating all the girls living there.

THE AMITYVILLE RISING

Genre: Action

A Sergeant from the Amityville Police Department must protect his son from Zombies, after a chemical explosion at a nearby Army base releases toxic gas into the air causing an acid rain that reanimate dead bodies.

THE BLACK STRING

Genre: Action

When a suburban slacker has a reckless encounter with a mysterious woman, his life begins to unravel in horrific fashion. His friends and family believe he’s losing his mind, but he’s convinced a cult of suburban, satanic witches have marked him for death.

THE BOY BEHIND THE DOOR

Genre: Thriller

After Bobby and his best friend Kevin are kidnapped and taken to a strange house in the middle of nowhere, Bobby manages to escape. But as he starts to make a break for it, he hears Kevin’s screams for help and realizes he can’t leave his friend behind.

THE STYLIST

Genre: Thriller/Horror

Obsession gets a makeover in The Stylist, a deliciously twisted slice of female-led psychological horror, nominated for the New Visions Award for Best Motion Picture at the 2020 Sitges International Film Festival and based on co-writer/director Jill Gevargizian’s award-winning short film of the same name.

THE GARDENER

Genre: Action/Thriller

An immigrant living a quiet life as a gardener at a manor house in England has to rely on old skills to save the family he works for from violent home invaders.

THE RANGER

Genre: Action

Teen punks, on the run from the cops and hiding out in the woods, come up against the local authority – an unhinged park ranger with an axe to grind.

TONE DEAF

Genre: Comedy, Horror, Thriller

A woman goes to the countryside to spend a quiet weekend after losing her job and having her last complicated relationship implode. She rents a country house from an old-fashioned widower, who struggles to hide his psychopathic tendencies.

TOTAL FRAT MOVIE

Genre: Comedy

Three years after a fraternity gets kicked off campus, Charlie and the remaining brothers must throw the greatest rush event ever to recruit a new pledge class and bring the house back to glory.

TRIGGERED

Genre: Action

Nine friends harbouring a dark secret are locked into explosive vests and pitted against each other in a grisly, last man standing deathmatch.
